
   #clyp-header {
            position: absolute;
        }

        .bottom-section,
        .top-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .background-container {
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .background-left {
            width: 100%;
            margin-right: -1px;
            display: none;
        }

        .top-section .background-left {
            height: 601px;
            background-image: linear-gradient(0deg, #38a8ae, #3cb9b2);
        }

        .bottom-section .background-left {
            height: 472px;
            background-image: linear-gradient(0deg, #39aeaf, #3bb6b1);
            margin-top: 33px;
        }

        .background-right {
            width: 100%;
            margin-left: -1px;
            display: none;
        }

        .top-section .background-right {
            height: 409px;
            background-image: linear-gradient(0deg, #23519a, #265c9c);
        }

        .bottom-section .background-right {
            height: 240px;
            background-image: linear-gradient(0deg, #24569b, #255b9c);
            margin-top: 265px;
        }

        .middle-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .background-center {
            max-width: 1440px;
            width: 100%;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .wavy-line-container {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .top-section .wavy-line-container {
            min-width: 900px;
        }

        .bottom-section .wavy-line-container {
            min-width: 1100px;
        }

        .hero-container {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            height: 100%;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-container-centered {
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

            .hero-container-centered .button.primary.tiny,
            .hero-container-centered .button.secondary.tiny {
                width: 100%;
                color: white;
                margin: 5px 0;
                font-size: 13px;
            }

            .hero-container-centered .button.secondary.tiny:hover {
                color: #3DBEB3;
            }

        .hero-headline {
            line-height: 1.1;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 12px 0;
        }

        .hero-sub-headline {
            margin: 13px 0 16px 0;
            font-weight: 100;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .homepage-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
        }

            .homepage-wrapper h1,
            .homepage-wrapper h2 {
                font-family: "BrandonGrotesque-Medium", sans-serif;
                font-weight: 500;
            }

        .feature-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #071827;
            margin: 18px 0;
        }

        .feature-description {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 100;
        }

        .feature-section {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1160px;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        .feature-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 20px 0 70px 0;
        }

        .feature-link {
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        svg .hide-on-mobile {
            display: none;
        }

        .feature-row.feedback .feature-icon {
            width: 150px;
        }

        .feature-row.easily-share .feature-icon {
            width: 150px;
            margin-left: -42px;
        }

        .feature-row.quality .feature-icon {
            width: 200px;
            margin-left: -64px;
        }

        .footer-headline {
            max-width: 420px;
            font-weight: normal;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        @media only screen and (min-width: 420px) {
            .hero-container-centered .button.primary.tiny,
            .hero-container-centered .button.secondary.tiny {
                width: 140px;
                margin: 6px;
            }

            .hero-headline {
                font-size: 32px;
            }

            .feature-section {
                padding: 0 40px;
            }

            .feature-title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .feature-description {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .feature-link {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        }

        @media only screen and (min-width: 768px) {
            .homepage-wrapper {
            }

            .hero-container-centered .button.primary.tiny,
            .hero-container-centered .button.secondary.tiny {
                font-size: 16px;
                width: 160px;
                height: 40px;
                line-height: 38px;
            }

            .hero-headline {
                font-size: 40px;
                margin: 12px 0;
            }

            .hero-sub-headline {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .top-section .hero-container-centered {
                margin-bottom: 13px;
            }

            .feature-content {
                align-self: center;
            }

            .feature-content,
            .feature-icon {
                width: 50%;
                padding: 0 13px;
            }

            .feature-title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .feature-row {
                padding: 40px 0;
                flex-direction: row;
            }

                .feature-row.feedback .feature-icon,
                .feature-row.easily-share .feature-icon,
                .feature-row.quality .feature-icon {
                    width: 50%;
                    margin-left: 0;
                }

                .feature-row.easily-share .feature-icon,
                .feature-row.quality .feature-icon {
                    order: 10;
                }

                .feature-row.easily-share .feature-content,
                .feature-row.quality .feature-content {
                    order: 0;
                }

            svg .hide-on-mobile {
                display: inline;
            }

            .footer-headline {
                max-width: 630px;
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (min-width: 1024px) {
            .hero-headline {
                font-size: 48px;
            }

            .hero-sub-headline {
                font-size: 24px;
                margin: 13px 0 24px 0;
            }

            .feature-title {
                font-size: 40px;
            }

            .feature-description {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .feature-link {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .feature-row {
                padding: 60px 0;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (min-width: 1440px) {
            .hero-container-centered .button.primary.tiny,
            .hero-container-centered .button.secondary.tiny {
                font-size: 16px;
                width: 180px;
                height: 48px;
                line-height: 46px;
                margin: 6px 12px;
            }

            .background-left {
                display: block;
            }

            .background-right {
                display: block;
            }

            .hero-headline {
                font-size: 60px;
                margin: 24px 0;
            }

            .hero-sub-headline {
                margin: 13px 0 40px 0;
            }

            .top-section .hero-container-centered {
                margin-bottom: 60px;
            }

            .feature-title {
                font-size: 48px;
            }

            .feature-section {
                padding: 0 16px;
            }

            .feature-content,
            .feature-icon {
            }
        }

        @font-face {
            font-family: 'BrandonGrotesque-Medium';
            src: url(data:application/font-woff;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('woff');
            font-weight: 500;
            font-style: normal;
        }
